"11:5:4" : {s: 11, a: 5, w: 4, r: "صدر", t: "صُدُورَهُمْ", l: "صَدْر", lc: 44, tl: "ṣudūrahum", lb: "বক্ষ, সিনা, অন্তর",e: "their breasts", b: "", f: 0, rm: "To return from, come back, proceed, issue or emanate from, go forward, advance or promote, come to pass, happen, emanate from, strike on the chest/breast, commence. Anything that fronts, or faces one; hence breast, chest or bosom [often meaning his mind]. The fore part of anything. Going, or turning back and away."},
